trans-unit.target: Ofrece compatibilidad en tiempo de diseño para los controles <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner" />.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner> is the base class for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner> and can be inherited to support custom implementations of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> controls.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner> es la clase base para <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner> y pueden ser heredados para admitir implementaciones personalizadas de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> controles.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner> extends its own base class, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebZoneDesigner>, by overriding the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A> method to hide the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.VerbStyle%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner> extiende su propia clase base, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebZoneDesigner>, reemplazando el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A> método para ocultar la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.VerbStyle%2A> propiedad.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the main purpose of this class for a control developer is that, unlike its parent, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner> has a public constructor so it can be inherited directly and used as a public implementation of the base class.
trans-unit.target: En caso contrario, el propósito principal de esta clase para un desarrollador de controles es que, a diferencia de su elemento primario, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner> tiene un constructor público para que pueda heredarse directamente y usar como una implementación pública de la clase base.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase" /> control associated with this designer.
Initializes an instance of the designer bound to the associated <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una instancia del diseñador enlazada al control <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase" /> asociado.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IDictionary" /> of the set of properties associated with the control.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.IDictionary" /> del conjunto de propiedades asociado al control.

trans-unit.source: Hides the <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.VerbStyle" /> property at design time.
trans-unit.target: Oculta la propiedad <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.VerbStyle" /> en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A> method overrides <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> to hide the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.VerbStyle%2A> property in the designer after calling the parent method.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A> reemplazos de método <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> para ocultar el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.VerbStyle%2A> propiedad en el diseñador después de llamar al método principal.

trans-unit.source: This is because the default <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> control does not render any zone-level verbs.
trans-unit.target: Esto es porque el valor predeterminado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> no representar los verbos de nivel de zona.

trans-unit.source: If you wish to render zone-level verbs in a derived class, you must override this method to not hide the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.VerbStyle%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Si desea representar los verbos de nivel de zona en una clase derivada, debe reemplazar este método para no ocultar la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.VerbStyle%2A> propiedad.
